合闸后的RL电路中的电流
RL电路的开关合闸后多少秒电流i达到它稳态值的一半

L*di/dt + R*i = V

di/dt + R/L * i = V/L

=>i(t) 	= V/R + C*e**(-R/L * t)
  i(0)	= V/R + C = 0
  C	= -V/R
  i(t)	= V/R - V/R*e**(-R/L * t)

  lim(t->∞) i(t) = V/R

  设i(th)	= V/R * 1/2
   V/(2*R)	= V/R - V/R * e**(-R/L * th)
   1/2		= 1 - e**(-R/L * th)
   e**(-th*R/L)	= 1/2
   -th*R/L	= ln(1/2)
   th*R/L	= ln(2)
   th		= L/R * ln(2)
